summary: A mod that adds the Divine of Wisdom and Logic into your Skyrim Game
descriptionHtml:
A mod that adds the Divine of Wisdom and Logic into your Skyrim Game
Note: He does not appear unless you spawn him with the developer console, Type in \"help Julianos 4\" into console to get his NPC code, the code I last saw was 08000D62 but It might be different so just check

Appearance Based off this image of him on a stain-glass window in Oblivion:
http://elderscrolls.wikia.com/wiki/Julianos

Inspired by my friend\'s Talos Mod
author: Ranzua
